## ✅ Example Usage

```rust
fn main() {
    let mut list = LinkedList::new();

    list.push_front(1);
    list.push_front(2);
    list.push_back(3);

    println!("List length: {}", list.len()); // 3

    println!("Popped front: {:?}", list.pop_front()); // Some(2)
    println!("Popped back: {:?}", list.pop_back());   // Some(3)
    println!("Popped front: {:?}", list.pop_front()); // Some(1)

    println!("List is empty: {}", list.is_empty()); // true
}
```

